# mutt-contrejour: base16-solarized for mutt
#
# These depend on mutt compiled with s-lang, not ncurses. Check by running `mutt -v`
# Details this configuration may be found in the mutt manual:
# ยง4.2 Patterns <http://www.mutt.org/doc/manual/manual-4.html#ss4.2>
# ยง3.7 Using color and mono video attributes <http://www.mutt.org/doc/manual/#color>

# https://www.neomutt.org/guide/configuration.html#color
#
# base00 - Default Background
# base01 - Lighter Background (Used for status bars)
# base02 - Selection Background
# base03 - Comments, Invisibles, Line Highlighting

# base04 - Dark Foreground (Used for status bars)
# base05 - Default Foreground, Caret, Delimiters, Operators
# base06 - Light Foreground (Not often used)
# base07 - Light Background (Not often used)

# base08 - Index Item: Deleted.
# base09 - Message: URL.
# base0A - Search Text Background. Message: Bold.
# base0B - Message: Code. Index Item: Tagged.
# base0C - Message: Subject, Quotes. Index Item: Trusted.
# base0D - Message: Headings.
# base0E - Message: Italic, Underline. Index Item: Flagged.
# base0F - Deprecated, Opening/Closing Embedded Language Tags e.g.

## Base
color normal      {{base05}}  {{base00}} # softer, bold

## Weak
color tilde       {{base03}}  {{base00}}  # `~` padding at the end of pager
color attachment  {{base03}}  {{base00}}
color tree        {{base03}}  {{base00}}  # arrow in threads
color signature   {{base03}}  {{base00}}
color markers     {{base03}}  {{base00}}  # `+` wrap indicator in pager

## Strong
color bold        {{base06}}  {{base00}}
color underline   {{base06}}  {{base00}}

## Highlight
color error       {{base08}}  {{base00}}
color message     {{base0d}}  {{base00}}  # informational messages
color search      {{base03}}  {{base0a}}
color status      {{base04}}  {{base02}}
color indicator   {{base06}}  {{base02}}  # inverse, brighter


# Message Index ----------------------------------------------------------------

## Weak
color index  {{base03}}  {{base00}}  "~R"        # read messages
color index  {{base03}}  {{base00}}  "~d >45d"   # older than 45 days
color index  {{base03}}  {{base00}}  "~v~(!~N)"  # collapsed thread with no unread
color index  {{base03}}  {{base00}}  "~Q"        # messages that have been replied to

## Strong
color index  {{base06}}  {{base00}}  "(~U|~N|~O)"     # unread, new, old messages
color index  {{base06}}  {{base00}}  "~v~(~U|~N|~O)"  # collapsed thread with unread

## Highlight
### Trusted
color index  {{base0c}}  {{base00}}  "~g"  # PGP signed messages
color index  {{base0c}}  {{base00}}  "~G"  # PGP encrypted messages
### Odd
color index  {{base08}}  {{base00}}  "~E"  # past Expires: header date
color index  {{base08}}  {{base00}}  "~="  # duplicated
color index  {{base08}}  {{base00}}  "~S"  # marked by Supersedes: header
### Flagged
color index  {{base0e}}  {{base00}}  "~F"       # flagged messages
color index  {{base0b}}  {{base00}}  "~v~(~F)"  # collapsed thread with flagged inside

# Selection
color index  {{base0b}}  {{base01}}   "~T"  # tagged messages
color index  {{base08}}  {{base01}}   "~D"  # deleted messages

